  "intent_precise": "78d33c-part-6.ot2.apiv2: Using Reservoir (reservoir, slot 5), plate2 (labware, slot Plate 2 at Rooom Temperature), mag_plate (plate, slot Mag Plate). With temperature module, magnetic module. (1) Pause: Please Refill the 300 uL Tip Box\n                     and Empty the Tip Waste (2) Pause: format (3) Disengage magnets to release beads. (4) Wait 1 seconds. (5) Mix 10 times at 64\u00b5L in column 0. (6) Incubate for 10 minutes. (7) Engage magnets at height_engagemm height for bead separation. (8) Pause for incubation. (9) Transfer 60\u00b5L from source to destination. (10) Wait 1 seconds. (11) Wait 0 seconds. (12) Wait 30 seconds. (13) Wait 0 seconds. (14) Disengage magnets to release beads. (15) Pause for incubation. (16) Transfer 22\u00b5L from source (multiple wells) to destination (multiple wells). (17) Incubate for 2 minutes. (18) Engage magnets at height_engagemm height for bead separation. (19) Pause for incubation. (20) Pause: Place a fresh 200 uL PCR plate on the temperature module. Resume. (21) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (22) Pause: DNA Post-PCR steps complete.",
